{"tid":2289560,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"智孝冧莊AAA人氣女星　BTS TWICE贏人氣歌手","createTime":"2020-11-17T10:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T13:53:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7be9c63eb133a5cddb0b4005d05e2362c6e527d9","tid":2289560,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"韓國演藝界盛事《Asia Artist Awards》 (AAA)將於下周三舉行，屆時將會頒發100%由網民參與票選的「人氣男女演員」及「人氣男女歌手」，票選活動於上月中至前日在網上展開，總票數多達38,909,129,617。<br />\n<br />\n勁爆韓團防彈少年團（BTS）力壓EXO、GOT7，與人氣女團TWICE各自獲得35.9%及34.9%票數榮膺「人氣男女歌手」得主，當中獲得最高票數的BTS更贏得「AAA Best of Best Starnews x最愛豆獎」，BTS先拔頭籌，連中兩元。<br />\n<br />\n「人氣男演員」方面，去年主演韓劇《會讀心術的那小子》的韓團GOT7成員Jr.於投票活動開始不久，已大熱拋離眾勁敵，最終以11.02%得票力壓李敏鎬及玄彬等勝出。至於去年贏得「人氣女演員」的宋智孝，以12.05%票數成功蟬聯，擊敗孫藝珍與徐睿知等女星。"},{"pid":"eac78d154d854d5448f29297f71379f4ede3d78c","tid":2289560,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"又bts<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46ff0928a22f8e9224b24ba60802c40994ec82d","tid":2289560,"uid":366997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"不如唔係bts 先出新聞<br />\n上年mama(我知呢個po講aaa) bts 攞晒4個大獎 我完全o嘴 今年應該又係全部獎都係bts"},{"pid":"167bcc3614b75cb923c40b03ebc45171ee7f244f","tid":2289560,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eac78d154d854d5448f29297f71379f4ede3d78c","tid":2289560,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:38:00.000Z","msg":"又bts<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"手足BTS<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d82a2af0ad424313d38f5f6a0980c58969f6ba7","tid":2289560,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T10:44:19.000Z","msg":"我淨係想睇Red velvet 同bts同埸<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">Seulgi x v世界第一</span></sp